Class YRCContentAssistData

  • java.lang.Object

    IYRCContentAssistData

    public abstract class YRCContentAssistData
extends java.lang.Object
implements IYRCContentAssistData
    The standard abstract implementation of an content IYRCContentAssistData.

    Subclasses must implement the getData method.
